    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Woke culture\" is a complex topic, and its impact is viewed very differently depending on one's perspective. Proponents see it as a crucial push for greater awareness and necessary changes to address systemic inequalities and historical injustices. Critics, however, argue that it has morphed into an intolerant environment that stifles open dialogue and promotes rigid ideological conformity. Ultimately, whether it serves social justice or becomes a form of censorship depends on how its principles are implemented in practice.",
