    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but isn't there a difference between public debate and actually pressuring institutions to deplatform or fire someone? it feels like some people use \"accountability\" as a label for whenever they just want to shut down an opinion they don't like. don't you think that's more about control than actual social justice?",
